\ ====================================================
\ assign patterns to characters
\ this is a big definItion but it is like a table of data
\ so it is reads easily but it is CODE.
\ *NEW* SET# calculates the set# for us

 DECIMAL
: CHANGE-CHARS ( -- )

   SAVE-CHARSET
